original_font_information.description:
Mustica Pro is a clean and geometric sans serif font that has a number of OpenType features and supports Latin, Cyrillic and Greek languages. 

The word Mustica has the meaning of a crown, even for Asians this word has a fairly broad meaning that is not limited to "crown". Mustika also has the meaning of being brave, clever or wise.

In this regard, the Mustica Pro font was carefully crafted with optimal effort, to make it a font that will be the choice of professionals.

Mustica Pro has many advantages apart from a fairly extensive language support. The important features in this font are case sensitive, ligatures, discretionary ligatures, proportional figures, tabular figures, oldstyle figures, proportional oldstyle, fraction, numerator, denominator, superscript, inferior, fractions, alignment colon and others.

With the many features that the Mustica Pro font has, it is hoped that this font will be one of the best choices for professionals.

Moreover, the complete family package includes hairline to black variables. For this reason, Mustica Pro is perfect to serve as the mainstay font for various design and commercial projects.
